    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Cream Is Cleaning Green,'' by Ruth La Ferla, (April 22):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Cream Is Cleaning Green,'' by Ruth La Ferla, (April 22):</p>
        <p>Sorry, but this party wasn't about cleaning green, but about being able to make gestures that cost little while enabling you to feel good about yourself, and morally superior to those who don't follow your example.</p>
        <p>Mary McLemore  Pike Road, Ala.</p>
      </block>
